Warren Buffett: Investor. Teacher. Icon. (CNBC May 2018)

warren buffett, Berkshire Hathaway, NYSE, NASDAQ, Wall Street, Finance, Stock, Stock Market, S&P500, Dow Jones, SPY, SPX, VOO, DJI, VIX, History, Economic, Benjamin Graham, American investor

Warren Buffett isn't just one of the most successful investors in history. He is also a teacher, whose financial advice and life lessons have influenced millions of people around the world.

This CNBC original documentary takes viewers inside the story of Warren Buffett’s extraordinary success and profiles some of the many people whose lives have been influenced, and even changed, by Buffett’s investment advice and life lessons.
